    "body": "Fixes #621\r\n\r\n* I have added a notification with all controls (like pause, play, stop)  as mentioned in #621 .\r\n* I have created (CoreServiceComponent, CoreServiceModule, CoreServiceScope) files for ```Injections``` like we have in app module (becasue we can not access app module in core. we can only access core module to app and custom module). this is necessary for this notification service. because we are accessing it into ```CoreReaderFragment``` which is part of ```core module``` (for accessing it into app and custom module) .\r\n* I have not removed any control from ```ReaderFragment``` yet (play, pause, stop button in ```ReaderFragment```). it is by default like earlier.\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/34593983/215765828-28688d81-ce0d-46a8-88d7-9f0013a4be64.mp4\r\n\r\n",
